Package codes.arrays

Class ArrayBreaker<T>

java.lang.Object
codes.arrays.ArrayBreaker<T>
Type Parameters:
T - Takes in the type of element fo the class.
All Implemented Interfaces:
ConversionTable<T>
public class ArrayBreaker<T> extends Object implements ConversionTable<T>
Class ArrayBreaker, implements interface ConversionTable which is used to get the row, column etc. of the single dimensional arrays and multi dimension arrays.
Author:
Trishit Maji
